Footnotes & Heritage

This LDM architecture inherits the legacy Crawler delivery system philosophy:

“One piece, no nonsense”

“Passive-first”

“Survive the Moon and keep going”

“If it fails, it dies quietly”

This continuity is intentional and beneficial for NASA/contractor reviewers.
